 - DNS installation
 - Internal_repo installation
 - Ansible inventory file for installation of ose 3
 - Proxy installation
 - OSE installation
    - git (copy for private network, clone for public network)
    - inventory copy

Phase 2
 - new ansible role for customization.
 - Checking network 
